I"(<p>Scrappy is basically a web scrapping framework written in Python. You can say it’s a complete full-fleged webscrapping tool.</p>

<p>In terms of learning prospective, it’s alot more complex than BeautifulSoup and Selenium and is harder to learn.</p>

<p>On the other hand, it’s complexity make it more efficient (faster) in terms of performance</p>

<p>When it comes to its working, generally databases are used in Scrappy.</p>

